A full image that can be burned to a microSD- card with minimum 32 gb storage as linked on the Project main page. Note, the image is only operational with specified hardware: Raspberry Pi 5, Real Time Clock Battery (rechargeable), RFID module PN532, RGB LED diod WS2812D and a PI camera module (ov5647/imx219/imx708)
Update to version 0.5.3 can be done with GUIApp_0_5_2_Pi5.tar.gz (needs the the full image version 0.5.2 to be installed first). 
